headline: Novo Nordisk, Google's Android, GE Healthcare: Trending Tickers
summary: Morning Brief host Julie Hyman tracks several of the day's top trending stock tickers, including Novo Nordisk's (NVO) positive trial results, the Financial Times reporting that China is dropping its antitrust probe into Alphabet's (GOOG, GOOGL) Android smartphones, and GE Healthcare Technologies (GEHC) exploring a stake sale of its Chinese business. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Morning Brief.
